.IX Item "file"
set the file name to use for the report; \f(CW%p\fR is expanded to the name
of the program, \f(CW%t\fR is expanded to a timestamp, \f(CW\*(C`%%\*(C'\fR is expanded
to a plain \f(CW\*(C`%\*(C'\fR
.IP "\fBlevel\fR" 4
